snippet.title: Amygdala - Teaser II
snippet.description:
#AMYGDALA #HORROR #INDIEGAME
Welcome to the haunting world of Amygdala, a l horror experience that explores the dark depths of the nightmare realm, manifested through incredible and terrifying creatures. Confront your deepest fears and uncover what lies behind the Amygdala. 

Prepare to immerse yourself in the sinister beauty of horror.
Wishlist now on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2453920/Amygdala/
